      >
        <div class="grid card bg-base-300 rounded-box place-items-center p-4">
          <p class="text-lg font-bold">
            "I haven't had this much fun doing software development in a long
            time and Spark.NET made it possible. I am rediscovering .NET and it
            is already informing my freelance work as well."
          </p>
          <br />
          <p class="text-sm">- G.P. Stone, Software Engineer</p>
        </div>
      </div>
