    </section>
    <section
      id="install"
      class="flex flex-col px-6 sm:px-8 container mx-auto max-w-5xl"
    >
      <div class="space-y-12">
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-black mx-auto max-w-2xl">
            <svg
              class="h-12 fill-accent"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              viewBox="0 0 440 440"
              ><path
                d="M172.5 414.9c-7.6-6.2 0-16.8.8-24.7 18.7-73.4 24.5-97.4 48.6-167.6-26.1.2-68.7-2.6-83-2.3s-28.7-2.1-21.9-16.4c21.2-47.2 45-91 71.1-135.3 7.8-13.6 14.7-27.8 23-41.1 3.5-5.6 13.6-6.5 17.8 3.2 4.2 9.6-1.3 30.1-1.2 39.8-3.4 25.7-15.6 58.6-19.9 84.1 27.7 2.8 55.5.8 83.5 2.4 11.3.8 29.4-2.4 32.8 7 3.5 9.4-10.3 25.4-16.5 35.2-18.9 26.6-35.3 53.9-52.4 81.8-25.1 40.5-43.9 80.1-65 123.2-2.7 7.2-9.2 16.5-17.7 10.7zm56.2-208.2c18.8-.9 12.1 16.3 7.9 27.3-12 35.2-20.6 61.8-30 97.7 27.8-55.7 61.1-109 97.4-159.3-25.9-.3-68.1-.5-91.1-1s-30.1 1.8-21-27c6.4-25 16.2-60.3 19.9-85.9-26.5 48.5-53.3 92.9-74.8 143.9 33-1.7 60 3.9 91.7 4.3z"
              ></path></svg
            >
            Create your first project
          </h2>
          <p
            class="text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-loose sm:leading-loose text-secondary-content"
          >
            Install the open source Spark CLI tool to get started and create
            your first project
          </p>
        </div>
        <InstallExample />
      </div>
      <VerticalDash />
      <div class="">
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-black mx-auto">
            <svg
              class="h-12 fill-accent"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              viewBox="0 0 440 440"
              ><path
                d="M172.5 414.9c-7.6-6.2 0-16.8.8-24.7 18.7-73.4 24.5-97.4 48.6-167.6-26.1.2-68.7-2.6-83-2.3s-28.7-2.1-21.9-16.4c21.2-47.2 45-91 71.1-135.3 7.8-13.6 14.7-27.8 23-41.1 3.5-5.6 13.6-6.5 17.8 3.2 4.2 9.6-1.3 30.1-1.2 39.8-3.4 25.7-15.6 58.6-19.9 84.1 27.7 2.8 55.5.8 83.5 2.4 11.3.8 29.4-2.4 32.8 7 3.5 9.4-10.3 25.4-16.5 35.2-18.9 26.6-35.3 53.9-52.4 81.8-25.1 40.5-43.9 80.1-65 123.2-2.7 7.2-9.2 16.5-17.7 10.7zm56.2-208.2c18.8-.9 12.1 16.3 7.9 27.3-12 35.2-20.6 61.8-30 97.7 27.8-55.7 61.1-109 97.4-159.3-25.9-.3-68.1-.5-91.1-1s-30.1 1.8-21-27c6.4-25 16.2-60.3 19.9-85.9-26.5 48.5-53.3 92.9-74.8 143.9 33-1.7 60 3.9 91.7 4.3z"
              ></path></svg
            >
            Everything you need to build fast
          </h2>
          <p
            class="text-lg max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-loose sm:leading-loose text-secondary-content"
          >
            Every spark project comes configured with all the essential features
            you need for a full stack web application.
          </p>
        </div>
        <VerticalDashMini />
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">Blazor SSR or Razor Pages</h3>
            <p
              class="max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-loose sm:leading-loose text-secondary-content"
            >
              An entire application configured and common pages scaffolded for
              you.
            </p>
          </div>
          <BlazorExample />
        </div>
        <VerticalDashMini />
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">Authentication & Authorization</h3>
            <p
              class="max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-loose sm:leading-loose text-secondary-content"
            >
              Protect your routes with an customizable authentication system
              already setup for you.
            </p>
          </div>
          <AuthExample />
        </div>
        <VerticalDashMini />
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">Entity Framework</h3>
            <p
              class="max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-loose sm:leading-loose text-secondary-content"
            >
              Spark comes with Entity Framework setup for you. Start reading and
              updating your data in minutes.
            </p>
          </div>
          <Efcore />
        </div>
        <VerticalDashMini />
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">Scheduled Jobs & Queues</h3>
            <p
              class="max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-loose sm:leading-loose text-secondary-content"
            >
              Background jobs and queues are essential to most applications.
              Spark comes with the Coravel job library installed and setup for
              you.
            </p>
          </div>
          <JobsExample />
        </div>
        <VerticalDashMini />
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">Email</h3>
            <p
              class="max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-loose sm:leading-loose text-secondary-content"
            >
              Quickly send emails using Spark's email provider.
            </p>
          </div>
          <EmailExample />
        </div>
        <VerticalDashMini />
        <div class="space-y-6 mb-24">
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">And much more</h3>
            <p
              class="max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-loose sm:leading-loose text-secondary-content"
            >
              Logging, database migrations, services, models, events, hosting...
            </p>
          </div>
          <a
            href="/docs/introduction"
            class="btn btn-accent btn-block sm:w-fit sm:btn-lg"
          >
            Get started
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
